'''Coert Beerman''' (born 1955) in [[Vlaardingen]] is a [[Netherlands|Dutch]] business man and currently [[Board of directors|member of the board]] of [[Feyenoord Rotterdam]] as well as the chairman of the [[Rabobank]] of the [[Rotterdam]] district. He also is the director of the [[Efteling]] and a member of the [[Economic Development Board]] Rotterdam. Before joining the Rabobank in the Rotterdam district he was the chairman of the Rabobank in the [[Eindhoven]] district. As a member of the board of directors at Feyenoord he is responsible for the financial [[portfolio (finance)|portfolio]].

